5%2Forg%2Fb14b2e86049cb18fc8bc2253e239a29f.jpg%2F9hmBQPm6gblih_D-CO3PRNo98GAKiF6xL8ksoQXJLKE&h=e5dd2afc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3548576/org/9572df1b3f6efe2acf59374ed03c136f.jpg/y3GzRD27TA5TCmyLLbsw4LZBT61sCCbL6AAfnsIAH54\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3548576%2Forg%2F9572df1b3f6efe2acf59374ed03c136f.jpg%2Fy3GzRD27TA5TCmyLLbsw4LZBT61sCCbL6AAfnsIAH54&h=61962558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3548632/org/2581ca593b7c64cd484810532eff6797.jpg/Yira2zP8HygNndyr4ETjYjaOz50K75XWI7UH6gm1B-o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3548632%2Forg%2F2581ca593b7c64cd484810532eff6797.jpg%2FYira2zP8HygNndyr4ETjYjaOz50K75XWI7UH6gm1B-o&h=9f524ec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3548694/org/1ff7a98862ab36a5747059741b47461b.jpg/TrAF8NKA8okga-bb0aqVgKwN69wMtbvnreKzVIfis1Q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3548694%2Forg%2F1ff7a98862ab36a5747059741b47461b.jpg%2FTrAF8NKA8okga-bb0aqVgKwN69wMtbvnreKzVIfis1Q&h=02ad261c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3548695/org/81898c21756360b5df94fcac8f9ffac8.jpg/V9C-8CcVyZlp-8FzoqkHREV9h9PLd2egM6sH2xmrB9s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3548695%2Forg%2F81898c21756360b5df94fcac8f9ffac8.jpg%2FV9C-8CcVyZlp-8FzoqkHREV9h9PLd2egM6sH2xmrB9s&h=0a3b726a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3548696/org/ed520bf012f0ecc48a4f4f2611565f48.jpg/6xlB6whyfDSvaVJhmPkgzzzDYc_jOPRh51hH981YR_c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3548696%2Forg%2Fed520bf012f0ecc48a4f4f2611565f48.jpg%2F6xlB6whyfDSvaVJhmPkgzzzDYc_jOPRh51hH981YR_c&h=75526471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3548698/org/6146e5664fb32f884768a077bc35dd1c.jpg/rsRa_KicfxUYvoHn3RBqcSxsVDxlkQEWGRIHBjMSBwY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3548698%2Forg%2F6146e5664fb32f884768a077bc35dd1c.jpg%2FrsRa_KicfxUYvoHn3RBqcSxsVDxlkQEWGRIHBjMSBwY&h=16a352ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3548765/org/a68dd3062011bfbf97ad191f17c52380.jpg/dOuVTL1lbuVs_aYS6BkDaBye3l0aGvcs1WKxiv9isYo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3548765%2Forg%2Fa68dd3062011bfbf97ad191f17c52380.jpg%2FdOuVTL1lbuVs_aYS6BkDaBye3l0aGvcs1WKxiv9isYo&h=c5638a0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3548766/org/31e9438760abf356fa55e69d5b293e90.jpg/xLJ2gs4Nb4Okd_FIlLhHkOPr7G_ehverGXFETzNxRE8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3548766%2Forg%2F31e9438760abf356fa55e69d5b293e90.jpg%2FxLJ2gs4Nb4Okd_FIlLhHkOPr7G_ehverGXFETzNxRE8&h=699c42fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示威者發起的全港三罷行動今日（13日）繼續，多區有堵路及縱火等。於傍晚，有示威者在於遮打道、雪廠街一帶設置路障，警方於晚上7時40分左右開始清場，先由裝甲車衝破德輔道中沿途路障，警方並使用胡椒球彈，防暴警及速龍小隊隨即落地展開追捕，有多人被捕，部分身穿恤衫或非黑色衣物，然後被押至中環戲院里附近，被要求頭向牆，其後再分批上警車及旅遊巴。據現場初步估算約有30人被捕。記者重返在警方押解被捕人士時曾逗留的小巷及蓬底，找到染血的紙巾、口罩、黑色背包，而地面留有血跡。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>由裝甲車開路　用胡椒球彈</strong><br />\n<br />\n下午約6時，有示威者在於遮打道、雪廠街設置路障。至晚上7時40分左右，有裝甲車衝破德輔道中沿途路障，速龍小隊拘捕一人，兩分鐘後，有現場消息指，警方曾施放胡椒球彈，不少人都要掩耳口鼻。防暴警其後向蘭桂坊方向推進，不少外籍人士咳嗽及流眼水，須由旁人助洗眼。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>戲院里大追捕　部分非黑衣人</strong><br />\n<br />\n防暴警中環戲院里附近拘捕多人，期間有部分被捕人士被要求「搭膊頭」，及被警呼喝「唔准仰高頭」等，最後被押至一個簷蓬底，環境幽暗，有警員要求被捕人坐在地下、頭部向牆，又不斷要求記者向後退，阻隔記者拍下過程。在拘捕行動期間，記者發現，有參與行動的防暴警，在服飾上展示「行動呼號」的位置，放裝了其他物件遮蓋其識別編號。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>分批押上警車、旅遊巴</strong><br />\n<br />\n然後被捕人士須分批上一架豬籠車及兩架旅遊巴，有部分被捕人士穿黑色衫、部分是上班族裝束，有外國人亦被捕。據記者現場觀察，在第一架旅遊巴上，被捕的外國人，其手機被警員拿走並嘗試對準該被捕人士的臉部，最後將手機放回其身上。其後該旅遊巴內部沒有燈光，記者無從觀察內裡情況。而第二架旅遊巴則有多名女性被捕。初步估算約有30人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>重返押解被捕人士小巷　地面留有血跡</strong><br />\n<br />\n在警方押走被捕人士後，記者重返警方曾處置被捕人士的中環戲院里小巷及簷蓬底，找到染血的紙巾、口罩、黑色背包，而地面留有血跡。至晚上9 時12分，警方出動吊臂車在中環清走路障，有交通警用掃帚掃街。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：王潔恩　鄭秋玲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/397962/11-13%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%B7-%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E5%A4%A7%E8%BF%BD%E6%8D%95-%E8%A3%9D%E7%94%B2%E8%BB%8A%E9%96%8B%E8%B7%AF-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%9130%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%BC%E4%B8%8A%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E5%B7%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F397962%2F11-13%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25BD%25B7-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25A3%259D%25E7%2594%25B2%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%259130%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258A%25BC%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25B7%25B4&d=jGmFyvXa%2BxCeqK61Wy4ey0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=bbb5d3ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/397962/11-13%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%B7-%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E5%A4%A7%E8%BF%BD%E6%8D%95-%E8%A3%9D%E7%94%B2%E8%BB%8A%E9%96%8B%E8%B7%AF-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%9130%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%BC%E4%B8%8A%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E5%B7%B4</a>"},{"pid":"97269a510f9f014ef072307ecb3b354d8495315c","tid":1717601,"uid":8566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"屌"}]}